metadata.name: 9/66+6 Re:guilty
metadata.description: In the pursuit of money for survival and pleasure, it is easy to loose it and forget what are the true values and where to find them. And then, clack, one moment and you find yourself deprived of freedom and, in general, of everything really meaningful in your life. Trying to regain life, you find new values for yourself, regain what you have lost, and the highest prize are experience and awareness of what you have not seen before right in front of your nose. I started my journey on the threshold of the prison cell and look where I am, going o out through the black door of the Metaverse, remembering everything that I neglected and of which I am guilty. Аминь
